  <brief_title>Study of Complication Rates Associated With PICC for Left vs Right</brief_title>
  <official_title>Assessment of Impact of Choice of Arm for Access on Rate of Complications in Peripherally Inserted Central Venous Catheters</official_title>
  <sponsors>
